getnewip (2.2.0-1) bionic; urgency=medium

  * Added
  * -----
  * > -v|--version for displaying version information.
  * > Extended compatibilty across distros (Ubuntu, Debian, Raspbian, Fedora, CentOS, openSUSE (Leap & Tumbleweed).
  *
  * Changed
  * -------
  * > Debian package description.
  * > unitName replaces gniUnit, to avoid confusion and match closer with uploadnewip.
  * > Root group now owns the unit config file, 0600 permissions.
  * > Test mode now overrides the same IP address (as it's supposed to).
  *
  * Fixed
  * -----
  * > Correctly written bash instructions.
  * > Now properly removes one or multiple given unit(s).
  * > Permissions for units, to avoid errors -- In some distros users don't have groups of the same name.

